  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK666">
<l>eṇṇiya veṇṇiyāṅ keytupa veṇṇiyār </l>
<l>tiṇṇiya rākap peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If those who have planned (an undertaking) possess firmness (in executing it) they will obtain what they have desired even as they have desired it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
